| Perseus | perseus |

## Output status.json Format

Each agent writes to their `output/status.json`:

```json
{
  "agent": "agent_id",
  "status": "completed",
  "startedAt": "2026-03-28T12:00:00Z",
  "completedAt": "2026-03-28T12:05:00Z",
  "elapsedMs": 300000,
  "summary": "Brief description of what was done",
  "outputFiles": ["file1.md", "file2.md"]
}
```
